hopobject.body: Looking for work cafergot rxlist Parcells showed his many sides during his unscripted 20-minute speech: He was philosophical, informative, educational, especially on the dynamics of life in the locker room; he was thankful to his ex-wife and three daughters for their support of a nomadic coaching life, and to the owners, players and coaches from his 19 years of being a head coach in the NFL and two stints as an executive.
